your indigenous territory.

00:29:45.790 --> 00:29:49.700
And let me preface
that also by saying

00:29:49.700 --> 00:29:53.230
I appreciate your wisdom
and your knowledge,

00:29:53.230 --> 00:29:54.480
my sweet elders.

00:29:54.480 --> 00:29:57.775
And I appreciate you letting
